{"title":"服务器应用搭建","uid":"3bcb9e0191441b82d91327554ec22c22","slug":"应用搭建","date":"2023-06-18T14:09:53.000Z","updated":"2023-06-18T14:09:53.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/应用搭建.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/database.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"应用搭建\"><a href=\"#应用搭建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"应用搭建\"></a>应用搭建</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-plain\" data-language=\"plain\"><code class=\"language-plain\">dnf module reset redis\ndnf module -y install redis:6\nsudo systemctl start redis\nsudo systemctl enable redis</code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://linuxhint.com/install-mysql-on-centos-8/\">How to Install MySQL on CentOS 8</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.niuqi360.com/mysql/how-to-create-a-new-user-in-mysql-and-grant-permissions/\">MySQL创建用户并赋予权限</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-mongodb-on-centos-8\">How To Install MongoDB on CentOS 8 | DigitalOcean</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-secure-mongodb-on-centos-8\">How To Secure MongoDB on CentOS 8 | DigitalOcean</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-configure-remote-access-for-mongodb-on-centos-8\">How To Configure Remote Access for MongoDB on CentOS 8 | DigitalOcean</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-nginx-on-centos-8\">How to Install Nginx on CentOS 8 | DigitalOcean</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.myfreax.com/how-to-install-apache-maven-on-centos-8/\">如何在CentOS 8安装Apache Maven</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/a256be592d20\">Centos8开放防火墙端口</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://feitam.es/how-to-fix-error-problem-with-installed-package-podman-and-buildah-installed-docker-ce-in-centos/\">How to fix error problem with installed package podman and buildah installed docker-ce in CentOS</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://computingforgeeks.com/install-docker-and-docker-compose-on-rhel-8-centos-8/\">install-docker-and-docker-compose-on-rhel-8-centos-8</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"禅道搭建\"><a href=\"#禅道搭建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"禅道搭建\"></a>禅道搭建</h1><p>禅道的搭建根据官方文档搭建即可<br><a href=\"https://www.zentao.net/book/zentaopms/360.html\">Centos8系统下安装httpd，mariadb，php7.2环境运行禅道</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"GitLab-搭建\"><a href=\"#GitLab-搭建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"GitLab 搭建\"></a>GitLab 搭建</h1><h2 id=\"安装步骤\"><a href=\"#安装步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装步骤\"></a>安装步骤</h2><ol>\n<li>升级服务器依赖<br><code>sudo yum -y update</code></li>\n<li>安装 GitLab 依赖<br><code>sudo yum -y install curl vim policycoreutils python3-policycoreutils</code></li>\n<li>安装 GitLab 邮件服务<br><code>sudo yum -y install postfix</code><br>安装完成后启动邮件服务<br><code>sudo systemctl enable postfix &amp;&amp; sudo systemctl start postfix</code></li>\n<li>添加 GitLab 的 CE Repository<br><code>curl -s https://packages.gitlab.com/install/repositories/gitlab/gitlab-ce/script.rpm.sh | sudo bash</code></li>\n<li>安装 GitLab CE<br><code>sudo yum install gitlab-ce</code></li>\n<li>配置 GitLab，修改 GitLab 的访问域名<br><code>sudo vi /etc/gitlab/gitlab.rb</code><br>将 <code>external_url &#39;http://gitlab.example.com&#39;</code>改为 GitLab 的域名或者 IP + 端口号</li>\n<li>更新 GitLab 配置<br><code>sudo gitlab-ctl reconfigure</code></li>\n<li>防火墙开放 http、https、ssh 访问<br><code>sudo firewall-cmd --permanent --add-service=&#123;ssh,http,https&#125; --permanent</code><br><code>sudo firewall-cmd --reload</code></li>\n<li>查看 root 用户的默认密码<br><code>cat /etc/gitlab/initial_root_password</code></li>\n<li>打开 GitLab 登录后修改密码即可</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"注意事项\"><a href=\"#注意事项\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意事项\"></a>注意事项</h2><p>CentOS 8 的源已经不维护了，所以在升级服务依赖前需要修改源</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cd &#x2F;etc&#x2F;yum.repos.d&#x2F;\nsed -i &#39;s&#x2F;mirrorlist&#x2F;#mirrorlist&#x2F;g&#39; &#x2F;etc&#x2F;yum.repos.d&#x2F;CentOS-*\nsed -i &#39;s|#baseurl&#x3D;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirror.centos.org|baseurl&#x3D;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;vault.centos.org|g&#39; &#x2F;etc&#x2F;yum.repos.d&#x2F;CentOS-*</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"参考链接\"><a href=\"#参考链接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考链接\"></a>参考链接</h2><p><a href=\"https://computingforgeeks.com/how-to-install-and-configure-gitlab-on-centos-rhel/\">Install and Configure GitLab on CentOS 8 &#x2F; RHEL 8</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"服务器搭建\"><a href=\"#服务器搭建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"服务器搭建\"></a>服务器搭建</h1><h2 id=\"搭建步骤\"><a href=\"#搭建步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搭建步骤\"></a>搭建步骤</h2><ol>\n<li>使用<code>rufus</code>制作一个<code>CentOS 8</code>的U盘启动盘</li>\n<li>启动服务器，启动时按<code>F11</code></li>\n<li>选择 U 盘启动</li>\n<li>选择安装<code>CentOS 8</code></li>\n<li>系统语言选择英文，中文可能出现乱码</li>\n<li>安装的内容选择<code>Server</code></li>\n<li>设置<code>root</code>账号的密码</li>\n<li>安装<code>CentOS</code>，安装完成后重启系统</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"注意事项-1\"><a href=\"#注意事项-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意事项\"></a>注意事项</h2><ol>\n<li>安装完成后需要修改网卡配置文件，把网络连接打开</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cd &#x2F;etc&#x2F;sysconfig&#x2F;network-scripts&#x2F;\nvi ifcfg-enp3s0</code></pre>\n\n<p>将 ONBOOT 改为 yes，然后执行 <strong>nmcli c reload</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"相关链接\"><a href=\"#相关链接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"相关链接\"></a>相关链接</h2><p>CentOS 8：<a href=\"https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/centos-vault/8.5.2111/isos/x86_64/\">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/centos-vault/8.5.2111/isos/x86_64/</a></p>\n<p>Rufus：<a href=\"https://rufus.ie/zh/\">https://rufus.ie/zh/</a></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"服务器应用搭建...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"编程","slug":"编程","count":17,"path":"api/categories/编程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":9,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">应用搭建</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\